  <brief_title>Metabolic Syndrome Risk Factor in IGT: STOP-NIDDM Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Metabolic Syndrome and Its Single Traits as Risk Factors of Diabetes in People With Impaired Glucose Tolerance: The STOP-NIDDM Trial</official_title>
