  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  High risk population

          -  Age 40 to 70 yrs.

          -  BMI &gt; 25 and &lt; 40; FPG &gt;5.5 mmol/l and &lt; 7.8 mmol/l; IGT in OGGT

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known type 2 diabetes

          -  Drug intake affecting glucose tolerance

          -  Any cardiovascular events within the last 6 months
      </textblock>
